{% extends 'proj/base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}About Black Jack Game{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
    <h1>About the Black Jack Game Project</h1>
    <p>This project is a web-based implementation of the classic card game Black Jack. The goal of the project is to create an interactive and fun gaming experience using modern web technologies.</p>
    <h2>Project Features</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Interactive Black Jack gameplay</li>
        <li>Stylish and user-friendly interface</li>
        <li>JSON API for game interactions</li>
        <li>ORM-based database integration</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Technologies Used</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Symfony Framework</li>
        <li>PHP and Twig</li>
        <li>JavaScript and AJAX</li>
        <li>Doctrine ORM</li>
    </ul>
{% endblock %}
